lead_paragraph: Lexi Thompson birdied the final hole for a four-under-par 68 and a share of the ANA Inspiration lead with Ai Miyazato on Friday in Rancho Mirage, Calif.

headline.main: Lexi Thompson and Ai Miyazato Tied at LPGA Event
